color.layout: colset NOTMOD = with notmod; (* used for non-modelled fields in packets *)

colset NDPrefixInformationOption = record Type              : Bit8   *
                                         Length            : NOTMOD *
                                         PrefixLength      : NOTMOD *
                                         L                 : Bit    * 
                                         (* on-link bit                      *)
                                         A                 : Bit    * 
                                         (* autonomous address configuration *)
                                         ValidLifetime     : UInt32 *
                                         PreferredLifetime : UInt32 *
                                         Prefix            : IPv6Prefix;

colset NDMTUOption = record Type   : Bit8  *
                           Length : NOTMOD *
                           MTU    : UInt32;

(* --- Router Soliciations --- *)

colset RouterAdvertisement = record CurHopLimit    : UInt8  *
                                   M              : Bit    * 
                                   (* Managed Address Configuration *)
                                   O              : Bit    * 
                                   (* Other Stateful Configuration  *)
                                   RouterLifetime : UInt16 *
                                   ReachableTime  : UInt32 *
                                   RetransTimer   : UInt32 *
                                   Options        : RAOptions;

(* ------------------------------------------------------------- *)

colset ICMPBody = union RS : RouterSolicitation     +
                       RA : RouterAdvertisement;

colset ICMPMessage = record Type : UInt8 *
                           Code : UInt8 *
                           Message : ICMPBody;

(* ------------------------------------------------------------- *)

colset IPv6Header = record Version            : Bit4     *                               
                          TrafficClass       : NOTMOD   *     
                          Flowlabel          : NOTMOD   *      
                          PayloadLenght      : NOTMOD   *      
                          NextHeader         : Bit8     *
                          HopLimit           : Bit8     *      
                          SourceAddress      : IPv6Addr * 
                          DestinationAddress : IPv6Addr;

colset Packet = union NOPACKET +
                     PACKET : IPv6Packet;

colset ERConfig = record ll_er : IPv6Addr *   (* link-local address of ER *)
                       er_l2 : LinkAddr;    (* link-addr of ER          *)

colset GWConfig = record ll_gwn : IPv6Addr *    (* link local address of GW *)
                        gwn_l2 : LinkAddr;     (* link-addr of GW          *)

ml.layout:
fun CreateRSWithPrefixes (gwconfig:GWConfig,
                          unsolicitedra:IPv6Packet,gwprefixes) =
    let
        val srcaddr = (#ll_gwn gwconfig)
        val destaddr = (#SourceAddress (#header unsolicitedra))
        val srclinkoption =
            CreateRSSrcLinkAddrOption (#gwn_l2 gwconfig)
        val rsprefixoption =
            List.map
            (fn (_,gwprefix) =>
             CreateRSPrefixOption (srcaddr,gwprefix))
            gwprefixes
    in
        CreateRS (srcaddr,destaddr,srclinkoption::rsprefixoption)
    end;

    List.filter

     (fn (RS_PrefixInformation {Prefix,A=0,L=1,...}) => Prefix
       | _ => "") Options)
  | GetRSGWPrefixes _ = [];

ml.layout:
fun FindAccepted (rs:IPv6Packet,gwprefixassign, bugfix1) =
    let
        val gw = (#SourceAddress (#header rs))
        val gwprefixnames = GetRSGWPrefixes rs

        val accepted =
            if (bugfix1)
                (* return all prefixes which edge router
                 has for that gateway *)
                then
                    List.map (fn (_,prefix) => prefix)
                      (List.filter
                       (fn (gw_ll,prefix) => (gw_ll = gw))
                       gwprefixassign)
            else
                List.filter
                (fn gwprefix =>
                 List.exists (fn (gw_ll,prefix) =>
                              gw_ll = gw andalso
                              prefix = gwprefix)
                 gwprefixassign)
                gwprefixnames
    in
        accepted
    end;

ml.layout:
fun CreateRAAssignNew (gwrs,erconfig:ERConfig,
                       prefixcount,gwprefixassign, bugfix1) =
    let
        val gwprefixes = GetRSGWPrefixes gwrs
        val srcaddr = (#ll_er erconfig)
        val accepted = FindAccepted (gwrs,gwprefixassign, bugfix1)
        val destaddr = (#SourceAddress (#header gwrs))
        val raprefixoptions =
            List.map CreateRAPrefixOptionAccept accepted
        val ranewprefixoption =
            CreateRAPrefixOptionNewPrefix prefixcount
    in
        CreateSolicitedRA
        (srcaddr,destaddr,ranewprefixoption::raprefixoptions)
    end;

ml.layout:
fun UpdateGWPrefixes (solicitedra,gwprefixes) =
    let
        val prefixoptions = RAGetPrefixOptions solicitedra

        val er_ll = (#SourceAddress (#header solicitedra))

        (* --- find newly asssigned prefixes --- *)
        val newprefixoptions =
            List.filter
            (fn (RA_PrefixInformation {Prefix,L=0,A=1,...}) => true
              | _ => false) prefixoptions;

        (* --- find names of new prefixes --- *)
        val newprefixnames =
            List.map
             (fn (RA_PrefixInformation {Prefix,L=0,A=1,...}) =>
              (er_ll,Prefix)
           | _ => ("","")) newprefixoptions;


        (* --- find updated prefixes --- *)
        val updprefixoptions =
            List.filter
            (fn (RA_PrefixInformation {Prefix,L=1,A=1,...}) => true
              | _ => false) prefixoptions;

        (* --- find prefixes from this ER still valid --- *)
        val updprefixnames =
            List.map
             (fn (RA_PrefixInformation
                     {Prefix,L=1,A=1,ValidLifetime=1,
                      PreferredLifetime=1,...}) => (er_ll,Prefix)
           | _ => ("","")) updprefixoptions;

    in
        newprefixnames^^
        (List.filter
         (fn (er_ll',gwprefix) =>
          (er_ll' <> er_ll) orelse
          (mem updprefixnames (er_ll',gwprefix)))
         gwprefixes)
    end;
